  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in the copper pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is lightly browned.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the beef shin pieces and cook until they are browned on all sides.",
    "Add the bhuna spice blend and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the tomato puree, coconut milk, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 2.5 hours.",
    "Remove the pot from the heat and let it cool slightly.",
    "Serve the curry hot, garnished with fresh cilantro."
